title: Phuquz - 2008 - Meat The Phuquz
description:
Phuquz (Pronounced /fuh-kuz/) 
"Meat the Phuquz"
2008
Abstract Infinity Records/Happiless Rhecords


Paul Rogers Keyboards/Voice
Jacob Painter Keyboards/Voice

Formed January 2008
Recorded January 2008
Disbanded January 2008



This is the back burner side project of Paul Rogers and Jacob Painter 
of "RunnuR". They claim that the band was only together for 36 minutes 
before they split due to creative differences. Here is their 31 minute
demo. The 5 minutes of arguing and hatred are not included, but 
pictures are.



01 - Alive
02 - Undoubtably Do
03 - John
04 - Lunatic Drone
05 - Turnaround
06 - The Beach
07 - Love Is The Question
08 - Akron


All songs written by Painter/Rogers
